Name: LifeCycle.KO_Narrative
nFORCE__Data__c:
In this section, I can have static narrative if there are components of my existing credit memo that never change.

  • I can also customize the format of the text within this field.
  • Using some useful editing components which have been incorporated for your convenience.
  • Things like FONT, SIZE, ITALICS, COLOR, and UNDERLINING can all be accomplished.

 

We can also insert charts and photos to accommodate details that may be stored in other components.

Name: LifeCycle.KO_Narrative
nFORCE__Data__c:
A lender or anyone in the credit process with the need to do so can add their commentary/recommendations in this section with formatting options to help make the text as meaningful as they would like.

 

We need to do this deal!

Name: LifeCycle.Default_Widget
nFORCE__View__c: <table class="table"> <tr> <th>Date</th> <th>Assigned To</th> <th>Actual Approver</th> <th>Status</th> <th>Comments</th> </tr> <!-- ko foreach: approvalHistory --> <!-- ko foreach: steps --> <tr> <td data-bind="dateText: theDate" /> <td> <span data-bind="text: originalActor.lastName" />, <span data-bind="text: originalActor.firstName" /> </td> <td> <span data-bind="text: assignedActor.lastName" />, <span data-bind="text: assignedActor.firstName" /> </td> <td data-bind="text: status" /> <td data-bind="text: comments" /> </tr> <!-- /ko --> <!-- /ko --> </table>
